# Frontend Documentation

This directory is reserved for future frontend-specific documentation such as:

- Angular component patterns
- State management strategies
- Styling conventions
- Performance optimization guides
- Frontend debugging guides

For now, frontend documentation can be found in:
- [Frontend CLAUDE.md](../../frontend/CLAUDE.md) - Angular patterns, component structure, debugging
- [E2E Testing](../e2e/README.md) - Playwright tests (includes frontend page objects and data-testid guide)
